	   <tr><td colspan=2>I have never heard anyone I met in game who has used this sword say anything about it proccing "Berserk." Honestly, I don't believe it does. Aside from that, I'd like to bring up the Warrior's Berserk threshold. Everyone seems to be saying that a Warrior will go Berserk when his/her health drops below 20%. Since I read that, I have been paying closer attention. I have noted that my Warrior will go Berserk when his health drops to 30%, and, when healing after the fight, will sometimes remain Berserk until almost 40% health. Is 20% the actual threshold for the Berserk ability?<br>&nbsp;<br>Aaranaf Surestroke<br>Warrior of the 26th season.</td></tr>
